
<link href='http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,100,300,500,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

<h2 style='font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: 100; line-height: 1.4;'>Hey <%= @resource.name %>!</h2>

<p style='font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif; font-weight: 100;'>Here is the link that you requested to change your password. You can do this by clicking below:</p>

<button style='font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif; padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 1.2em; line-height: 1.3333333; border-radius: 6px; color: #fcfcfc; background: #5bc0de; border: 1px solid #46b8da;'><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), style: 'text-decoration: none; color: #fcfcfc;' %></button>

<p style='font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif; font-weight: 100;'>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p style='font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif; font-weight: 100;''>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
<p style='font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif; font-weight: 100;'>Your secret admirer,</p>
<h2 style='font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif; font-weight: 200;'>Nathan Allen</h2>